      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute gem! This car is in pristine, showroom condition and looks like it just rolled off the assembly line. It has been meticulously cared for, offering a flawless driving experience and a spotless interior that's truly rare to find. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you!",
