    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a reliable daily driver who isn't concerned with a perfect exterior. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been consistently maintained. However, the body shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that performs well on the road, even if it isn't a showpiece.",
