    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm super excited to find a new home for my car. It's in really solid shape and has been a total joy to drive! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-taken care of, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you. It\u2019s got a great look and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin. Feel free to message me with any questions!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering featuring the S65 4.0L V8. This high-revving unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission for maximum engagement. The drivetrain is anchored by a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent technical servicing includes proactive rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, addressing key platform-specific maintenance. The suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics, providing sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. While the exterior reflects its status as a dedicated driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals and chassis rigidity remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
