    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic coat that still catches the light beautifully; while there are a few minor rock chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, you will find a pristine, smoke-free environment. The leather upholstery has been treated regularly, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, while the carpets and headliner remain spotless. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom, including the ice-cold air conditioning and the premium sound system. Mechanically, this car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at every recommended interval. The brakes are firm, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. This car represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a high-quality, dependable vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 31500.0,
